Hope, you find my work usefull.

Here is some default bindings:

Crtl+modkey+s - tag manipulation submenu (rename, add, del, etc)

altkey+F1 - jump to one tag left
altkey+F2 - jump to one tag right

modkey+F1 - move current clinet one tag left
modkey+F2 - move current clinet one tag right

Mail bugs to ierton@gmail.com.
Sergey.
